00:41:31.870 --> 00:41:34.450
the language of adaptive
performance and TOMO

00:41:34.450 --> 00:41:36.980
with your team so that
your whole team can

00:41:36.980 --> 00:41:40.710
be involved in creating a
high performing culture.

00:41:40.710 --> 00:41:42.210
Once you start to
talk about it, you

00:41:42.210 --> 00:41:43.920
