00:42:12.560 --> 00:42:15.460
This is a way to kick-start
your conversations about play,

00:42:15.460 --> 00:42:17.080
purpose, and potential.

00:42:17.080 --> 00:42:19.560
We hold weekly reflection
huddles in our firm

00:42:19.560 --> 00:42:21.460
and many of the
organizations we work with,

00:42:21.460 --> 00:42:23.660
